NEW precursor.301.a.desc:0 "Intercepted communications from a group of independent prospectors indicate that they recently found something relating to an ancient Precursor civilization on §H[precursor_planet.GetName]§!. Superstition compelled them to leave the [precursor_planet.GetPlanetMoon] alone, so whatever they discovered must still be there."
OLD precursor.301.a.desc:0 "Intercepted communications from a group of independent prospectors indicate that they recently found something relating to an ancient Precursor civilization on [precursor_planet.GetName]. Superstition compelled them to leave the [precursor_planet.GetPlanetMoon] alone, so whatever they discovered must still be there."
CN  precursor.301.a.desc:0 "我们从一队独立勘探者处截获的通讯表明，他们最近在[precursor_planet.GetName]发现了与远古先驱文明相关的物品。出于迷信，他们并没有染指[precursor_planet.GetPlanetMoon]，因此他们发现的东西现在应该还在原处。"
NEW precursor.301.b.desc:0 "Several merchant ships passing in the vicinity of §H[precursor_planet.GetName]§! have independently of each other reported anomalous readings coming from the direction of the [precursor_planet.GetPlanetMoon]. After studying these readings, experts on [Root.Capital.GetName] believe they may be indicative of ancient Precursor activity."
OLD precursor.301.b.desc:0 "Several merchant ships passing in the vicinity of [precursor_planet.GetName] have independently of each other reported anomalous readings coming from the direction of the [precursor_planet.GetPlanetMoon]. After studying these readings, experts on [Root.Capital.GetName] believe they may be indicative of ancient Precursor activity."
CN  precursor.301.b.desc:0 "数艘行经[precursor_planet.GetName]附近的商船在没有互相联系的情况下都报告称在[precursor_planet.GetPlanetMoon]方向检测到了异常的数据。在对数据进行研究后，[Root.Capital.GetName]专家认为，这是远古先驱活动造成的现象。"
NEW precursor.301.d.desc:0 "Several recruits from our ground forces recently made a HALO insertion onto the surface of §H[precursor_planet.GetName]§! as part of a survival training exercise. When the recruits were picked up again after two months, one of them reported several findings indicating that an ancient Precursor civilization had a presence on this world long ago."
OLD precursor.301.d.desc:0 "Several recruits from our ground forces recently made a HALO insertion onto the surface of [precursor_planet.GetName] as part of a survival training exercise. When the recruits were picked up again after two months, one of them reported several findings indicating that an ancient Precursor civilization had a presence on this world long ago."
CN  precursor.301.d.desc:0 "我方地面部队的几名新兵最近在训练中使用HALO降落在[precursor_planet.GetName]地表。两个月后接应新兵时，有一名新兵报告称发现了许多很久以前就有先驱文明踏足这个星球的证据。"
ADD precursor.301.e.desc:0 "Diagnostic Array Theta has registered a possible irregularity on §H[precursor_planet.GetName]§!. No [Root.GetSpeciesAdj] units are known to be operating in the vicinity of this uninhabited astronomical body, but a preliminary analysis indicates that it may have been visited by a Precursor civilization at some point in the distant past."
ADD precursor.301.f.desc:0 "Patrol drones performing a routine surface sweep of §H[precursor_planet.GetName]§! have alerted the Mind to an irregularity within our controlled space. Signs of possible activity consistent with a Precursor civilization have been sighted."
