ADD precursor.310.desc:0 "A private collector on [collector_home.GetName] has somehow come into ownership of an ancient Precursor artifact believed to be [Root.GetPrecursorCiv] in origin. Despite government pressure, the collector has so far been reluctant to part with it."
ADD precursor.310.a:0 "Everyone has a price."
ADD precursor.310.b:0 "It belongs in a museum!"
ADD precursor.310.c:0 "Let the collector keep it."
ADD buy_precursor_artifact:0 "Buy the artifact for an exorbitant sum.\n\n"
ADD seize_precursor_artifact:0 "Declare the artifact to be state property and have it seized by the local authorities.\n\n"
